long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Automatic proxy socks5 (or manual), and open amazon

Automatic proxy:

You can use the socks proxy function after installing the plug-in.

The first time you install the plug-in, the following URL will be automatically opened: https://portal.aws.amazon.com/gp/aws/developer/registration/index.html?nc2=h_ct&src=header_signup
Manually modify the proxy:

Click the plug-in icon to enter the proxy setting interface.

Fill in the proxy host and port in the setting interface.

Click the "Modify" button to save the settings.
Currently only supports Socks5 proxy type.
